Installation:

    git clone https://github.com/DeathRay1977/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/.vimrc ~/.vimrc
    
    Start up vim and do 
        :PlugClean
        :PlugUpdate
        
    To get YouCompleteMe working (IntelliJ style completion)
    
        $ cd ~/.vim/Plugged/YouCompleteMe
        $ python install.py
    


